casebody.head_matter:
Briand WILLIAMS, Petitioner
v.
CALIFORNIA
No. 18-9186
Supreme Court of the United States.
October 7, 2019
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for a writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeal of California, Second Appellate District dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
